This is the start of project &lt;i&gt;graeae&lt;/i&gt; - named after the &lt;a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Graeae"&gt;three sisters&lt;/a&gt; of Greek mythology who were sisters to the gorgons and shared one eye and one tooth between them. This is a place where I'll stick the code that I end up using in more than one project that is convenient, but not really substantial enough to make into separate projects.
